al-Din_Yildiz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taj_al-Din_Yildiz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nod\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"all five judges\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"the third round\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"start\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"finish\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"scores\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the only split decision victory for Petecio in the tournament after she won her first four bouts either via unanimous decision or stoppage.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only split decision victory\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"Petecio\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"her first four bouts\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"unanimous decision\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"stoppage\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, it was enough for the pride of Davao del Sur to reach the Olympics for the second straight edition and get a crack at completing herunfinished businessafter falling short of the gold in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davao_del_Sur\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.506207533843975e-21, \"text\": \"Davao del Sur\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davao_del_Sur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davao_del_Sur\"}, {\"begin\": 1493, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9379920380378037e-14, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pride\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"the second straight edition\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"a crack\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"herunfinished businessafter\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Villegas survived Bulgaria's Zlatislava Chukanova for a top-four finish in the women's 50kg class via unanimous decision, 5-0, but not after a tight contest that saw three of the five judges settle for a tie, with the other two scoring in favor of the Filipina.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999986486618617, \"rank\": 1.3512386447960906e-06, \"text\": \"Bulgaria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1764, \"end\": 1772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999919634965466, \"rank\": 8.036568231379341e-06, \"text\": \"Filipina\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Villegas\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"a top-four finish\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 50kg class\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"unanimous decision\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"a tight contest\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"the five judges\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"a tie\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"the other two scoring\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"favor\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villegas unanimously won the first two rounds, but she incurred a one-point penalty for holding as she left the comeback door ajar for Chukanova.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Villegas\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"the first two rounds\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-point penalty\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"the comeback door\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"ajar\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"Chukanova\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic ticket appeared to slip out of Villegas' hands when she got knocked down in the third round after a right straight to the head from Chukanova, but the pride of Leyte brushed the fall off and finished the fight.\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2094, \"end\": 2099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leyte\", \"score\": 0.9999999556871454, \"rank\": 4.3357113503809415e-08, \"text\": \"Leyte\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leyte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leyte\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic ticket\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"Villegas' hands\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"the third round\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"a right straight\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"Chukanova\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2075}, {\"ngram\": \"the pride\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"the fall\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villegas even got the nod of two judges in the third round as she sealed her spot for her Olympic debut, 29-27, 29-27, 28-28, 28-28, 28-28.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Villegas\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"the nod\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"two judges\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"the third round\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"her spot\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic debut\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to rules set by the Paris 2024 Boxing Unit, in the case three or more judges have even scores, they are requested to pick a winner.\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.942449971780714e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2328, \"end\": 2334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 0.9999998567768773, \"rank\": 1.4322302963811048e-07, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rules\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"three or more judges\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"even scores\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"a winner\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villegas won the tiebreak.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Villegas\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"the tiebreak\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Petecio and Villegas will join fellow boxerEumir Marcialin Paris, increasing the Philippines' athlete roster for the Olympics to six.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2516, \"end\": 2521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org